messages.content: Oh my God, somebody's shooting at the sheriff's department!
Yes, I'm hiding across the street. Please get the cops here right now!
Somebody's shooting all around. I'm on the street.
Oh my God, they're still shooting!
Okay, I have somebody on the way there, but I need to know what he looks like.
I don't know, I can't see. It's really dark. He's in the parking lot and he's shooting.
Oh my God, oh my God, please hurry!
Do you know where exactly it's coming from?
There's just somebody walking around in the parking lot.
He's just walking around and I'm right across the street. I don't want him to come to my house.
I know, we have a whole bunch of people on the way there.
I have to let you go though because we have multiple 9-1-1 calls. Okay? Stay safe.
